            "metadata": [
              {
                "app_version": "v0.73.0",
                "chart": "kube-prometheus-stack",
                "first_deployed": 1780645977,
                "last_deployed": 1780645977,
                "name": "kube-prometheus-stack",
                "namespace": "monitoring",
                "notes": "kube-state-metrics is a simple service that listens to the Kubernetes API server and generates metrics about the state of the objects.\nThe exposed metrics can be found here:\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/kube-state-metrics/blob/master/docs/README.md#exposed-metrics\n\nThe metrics are exported on the HTTP endpoint /metrics on the listening port.\nIn your case, kube-prometheus-stack-kube-state-metrics.monitoring.svc.cluster.local:8080/metrics\n\nThey are served either as plaintext or protobuf depending on the Accept header.\nThey are designed to be consumed either by Prometheus itself or by a scraper that is compatible with scraping a Prometheus client endpoint.\n\n1. Get the application URL by running these commands:\n  export POD_NAME=$(kubectl get pods --namespace monitoring -l \"app.kubernetes.io/name=prometheus-node-exporter,app.kubernetes.io/instance=kube-prometheus-stack\" -o jsonpath=\"{.items[0].metadata.name}\")\n  echo \"Visit http://127.0.0.1:9100 to use your application\"\n  kubectl port-forward --namespace monitoring $POD_NAME 9100\nkube-prometheus-stack has been installed. Check its status by running:\n  kubectl --namespace monitoring get pods -l \"release=kube-prometheus-stack\"\n\nVisit https://github.com/prometheus-operator/kube-prometheus for instructions on how to create \u0026 configure Alertmanager and Prometheus instances using the Operator.\n\n1. Get your 'admin' user password by running:\n\n   kubectl get secret --namespace monitoring kube-prometheus-stack-grafana -o jsonpath=\"{.data.admin-password}\" | base64 --decode ; echo\n\n\n2. The Grafana server can be accessed via port 80 on the following DNS name from within your cluster:\n\n   kube-prometheus-stack-grafana.monitoring.svc.cluster.local\n\n   Get the Grafana URL to visit by running these commands in the same shell:\n   NOTE: It may take a few minutes for the LoadBalancer IP to be available.\n        You can watch the status of by running 'kubectl get svc --namespace monitoring -w kube-prometheus-stack-grafana'\n     export SERVICE_IP=$(kubectl get svc --namespace monitoring kube-prometheus-stack-grafana -o jsonpath='{.status.loadBalancer.ingress[0].ip}')\n     http://$SERVICE_IP:80\n\n3. Login with the password from step 1 and the username: admin\n#################################################################################\n######   WARNING: Persistence is disabled!!! You will lose your data when   #####\n######            the Grafana pod is terminated.                            #####\n#################################################################################\n",
                "revision": 1,
                "values": "{\"alertmanager\":{\"enabled\":false},\"grafana\":{\"adminPassword\":\"Siseon2026!\",\"dashboardProviders\":{\"dashboardproviders.yaml\":{\"apiVersion\":1,\"providers\":[{\"disableDeletion\":true,\"editable\":false,\"folder\":\"📊 인프라 모니터링\",\"name\":\"infra-templates\",\"options\":{\"path\":\"/var/lib/grafana/dashboards/infra-templates\"},\"orgId\":1,\"type\":\"file\"},{\"disableDeletion\":true,\"editable\":true,\"folder\":\"📊 인프라 모니터링\",\"name\":\"infra-custom\",\"options\":{\"path\":\"/var/lib/grafana/dashboards/infra-custom\"},\"orgId\":1,\"type\":\"file\"}]}},\"dashboards\":{\"infra-custom\":{\"stockops-infra\":{\"json\":\"{\\\"panels\\\":[{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"max\\\":100,\\\"min\\\":0,\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"yellow\\\",\\\"value\\\":60},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"red\\\",\\\"value\\\":80}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"percent\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":0,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":1,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"100 - (avg(irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode='idle'}[5m])) * 100)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"CPU\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"🖥️ 클러스터 CPU 사용률\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"gauge\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"max\\\":100,\\\"min\\\":0,\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"yellow\\\",\\\"value\\\":60},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"red\\\",\\\"value\\\":80}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"percent\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":4,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":2,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"100 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes * 100)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"Memory\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"💾 클러스터 메모리 사용률\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"gauge\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"short\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":8,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":3,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"count(kube_pod_status_phase{phase='Running'})\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"Running\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"✅ Running Pods\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"stat\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"red\\\",\\\"value\\\":1}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"short\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":12,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":4,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"count(kube_pod_status_phase{phase='Failed'}) or vector(0)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"Failed\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"🚨 Failed Pods\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"stat\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"blue\\\",\\\"value\\\":null}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"short\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":16,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":5,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"count(kube_node_info)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"Nodes\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"🖧 Node 수\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"stat\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"yellow\\\",\\\"value\\\":1}]},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"short\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":5,\\\"w\\\":4,\\\"x\\\":20,\\\"y\\\":0},\\\"id\\\":6,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"count(kube_pod_status_phase{phase='Pending'}) or vector(0)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"Pending\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"⏳ Pending Pods\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"stat\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":3,\\\"w\\\":24,\\\"x\\\":0,\\\"y\\\":5},\\\"id\\\":7,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"kube_pod_status_phase{namespace='stockops'}\\\",\\\"instant\\\":true,\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}} - {{phase}}\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"📋 StockOps 서비스별 Pod 상태\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"table\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"custom\\\":{\\\"fillOpacity\\\":15,\\\"lineWidth\\\":2},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"percent\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":0,\\\"y\\\":8},\\\"id\\\":8,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"sum(rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{namespace='stockops',container!=''}[5m])) by (pod) * 100\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}}\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"⚡ StockOps Pod CPU 사용률\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"timeseries\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"custom\\\":{\\\"fillOpacity\\\":15,\\\"lineWidth\\\":2},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"bytes\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":12,\\\"y\\\":8},\\\"id\\\":9,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"sum(container_memory_working_set_bytes{namespace='stockops',container!=''}) by (pod)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}}\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"💡 StockOps Pod 메모리 사용량\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"timeseries\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"custom\\\":{\\\"fillOpacity\\\":15,\\\"lineWidth\\\":2},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"binBps\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":0,\\\"y\\\":14},\\\"id\\\":10,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"sum(rate(container_network_receive_bytes_total{namespace='stockops'}[5m])) by (pod)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}} RX\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"📥 네트워크 수신 트래픽\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"timeseries\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"custom\\\":{\\\"fillOpacity\\\":15,\\\"lineWidth\\\":2},\\\"unit\\\":\\\"binBps\\\"}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":12,\\\"y\\\":14},\\\"id\\\":11,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"sum(rate(container_network_transmit_bytes_total{namespace='stockops'}[5m])) by (pod)\\\",\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}} TX\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"📤 네트워크 송신 트래픽\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"timeseries\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":0,\\\"y\\\":20},\\\"id\\\":12,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"sum(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace='stockops'}) by (pod)\\\",\\\"instant\\\":true,\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{pod}}\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"🔄 Pod 재시작 횟수\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"table\\\"},{\\\"datasource\\\":{\\\"type\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"prometheus\\\"},\\\"fieldConfig\\\":{\\\"defaults\\\":{\\\"thresholds\\\":{\\\"mode\\\":\\\"absolute\\\",\\\"steps\\\":[{\\\"color\\\":\\\"green\\\",\\\"value\\\":null},{\\\"color\\\":\\\"red\\\",\\\"value\\\":0}]}}},\\\"gridPos\\\":{\\\"h\\\":6,\\\"w\\\":12,\\\"x\\\":12,\\\"y\\\":20},\\\"id\\\":13,\\\"targets\\\":[{\\\"expr\\\":\\\"kube_node_status_condition{condition='Ready',status='true'}\\\",\\\"instant\\\":true,\\\"legendFormat\\\":\\\"{{node}}\\\"}],\\\"title\\\":\\\"🟢 Node 상태\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"table\\\"}],\\\"refresh\\\":\\\"30s\\\",\\\"schemaVersion\\\":38,\\\"tags\\\":[\\\"stockops\\\",\\\"infra\\\",\\\"custom\\\"],\\\"time\\\":{\\\"from\\\":\\\"now-1h\\\",\\\"to\\\":\\\"now\\\"},\\\"timezone\\\":\\\"Asia/Seoul\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"🏭 StockOps 인프라 현황\\\",\\\"uid\\\":\\\"stockops-infra-custom\\\"}\"}},\"infra-templates\":{\"kubernetes-cluster\":{\"datasource\":\"Prometheus\",\"gnetId\":7249,\"revision\":1},\"kubernetes-pods\":{\"datasource\":\"Prometheus\",\"gnetId\":6417,\"revision\":1},\"node-exporter-full\":{\"datasource\":\"Prometheus\",\"gnetId\":1860,\"revision\":37}}},\"datasources\":{\"datasources.yaml\":{\"apiVersion\":1,\"datasources\":[{\"isDefault\":true,\"name\":\"Prometheus\",\"type\":\"prometheus\",\"uid\":\"prometheus\",\"url\":\"http://kube-prometheus-stack-prometheus:9090\"},{\"jsonData\":{\"authType\":\"default\",\"defaultRegion\":\"ap-northeast-2\"},\"name\":\"CloudWatch\",\"type\":\"cloudwatch\",\"uid\":\"cloudwatch\"}]}},\"enabled\":true,\"persistence\":{\"enabled\":false},\"service\":{\"type\":\"LoadBalancer\"},\"sidecar\":{\"datasources\":{\"defaultDatasourceEnabled\":false}}},\"kubeStateMetrics\":{\"enabled\":true},\"nodeExporter\":{\"enabled\":true},\"prometheus\":{\"enabled\":true,\"prometheusSpec\":{\"resources\":{\"limits\":{\"cpu\":\"500m\",\"memory\":\"512Mi\"},\"requests\":{\"cpu\":\"100m\",\"memory\":\"256Mi\"}},\"retention\":\"7d\"}}}",
